Requirements:
  ruby 1.9.2+, curl, vmc 0.1.3.6.beta5+
HOWTO
  Configure: Edit the config file
  Test: You could execute the script test.sh or follow these steps by yourself.
    Create users for test
      run.sh create_user
    Test and verify
      run.sh create_app && run.sh load_app
    OR
      run.sh create_app && run.sh funload_app
NOTE
   run.sh start_app:   may exhaust your DEAs if you have no enough DEAs
   run.sh funload_app: use this to load data if you have no enough DEAs
Delete apps/services/users
   purge.sh

